title: vivo Y33s (Midday Dream, 128 GB)  (8 GB RAM)

product_specification.In The Box: Handset, Earphone, USB Cable, Charger, Sim Eject Tool, Phone Case, Protective Film, Documentation
product_specification.Other Display Features: 20:09 Aspect Ratio, 90.60% Screen-to-Body Ratio, Panda Glass
product_specification.Primary Camera Features: Triple Rear Camera Setup: 50MP (f/1.8) + 2MP (f/2.4) + 2MP (f/2.4), Primary Camera Features: Photo, Portait, Night, Pano, Live Photo, Slo-mo, Time-lapse, Pro, Doc
product_specification.Secondary Camera Features: 16MP Front Camera (f/2.0), Features: Photo, Portait, Night, Live Photo
product_specification.Sensors: Accelerometer, Ambient Light Sensor, Proximity Sensor, E-compass, Fingerprint Sensor (Side), Gyroscope
product_specification.Other Features: Ultra Game Mode, Face Access, Eye Protection Mode, Multi-Turbo 5.0, AI Editor, iManager, 18W Fast Charging
product_specification.Audio Formats: WAV, MP3, MP2, MIDI, Vorbis, APE, FLAC
product_specification.Warranty Summary: 1 Year for Handset and 6 Months for In-box Accessories

product_description.8 mm Ultra-slim Body: This is a sleek and slim smartphone featuring a 2.5D flat frame on an 8 mm thin body. Also, it is a lightweight smartphone that you can carry around comfortably.
product_description.FHD+ Screen with Eye Protection: The Vivo Y33s features a 16.71 cm (6.58) FHD+ in-cell display that offers vibrant shades with vivid details. So, you get to see stunning visuals while enjoying your favourite shows and games on this smartphone that also features a built-in blue light filter to protect your eyes.
product_description.50 MP Main Camera with Eye Auto focus: Capture pristine, clear, high-resolution photos with the 50 MP Main Camera with Eye Auto focus of this Vivo smartphone.
product_description.16 MP Super Night Selfie: The 16 MP front camera clicks HD selfies and makes you feel confident with every single photo, thanks to its portrait algorithm.
product_description.EIS Ultra Stable Video: This smartphone comes with an automatic rear camera EIS to ensure that you capture steady videos without any shake or blur.
product_description.Super Night Mode: This is a noise reduction technology that brings together multiple frames in one to offer high purity and clarity. So, you can capture the stunning beauty of night using this smartphone.
product_description.Helio G80 Processor with 128 GB Expandab: The Helio G80 octa-core processor supported by CPU clock speeds of up to 2.0 GHz ensures high-speed, seamless performance. Also, to let you store photos, apps, files, and much more; this Vivo phone has 128 GB storage capacity that can be expanded up to 1 TB, thanks to its triple card slot support.
product_description.8 GB + 4 GB Extended RAM: Apart from the 8 GB memory, this smartphone has up to 4 GB of ROM space, which you can use as extended RAM for seamlessly switching between various apps.
product_description.5000 mAh Battery and 18W Fast Charge: The 5000mAh battery, 18W Fast Charge, and Vivo Energy Guardian (VEG) ensure that your smartphone is up and running. Also, it has a reverse charging function that lets you use it as a power bank.
product_description.Side Fingerprint Sensor and Face Wake: The power button of this smartphone has a powerful fingerprint scanner to unlock this device quickly. This smartphone also has a Face Wake feature that lets you unlock it with a blink of an eye.
product_description.Ultra Game Mode: This mode offers a complete sensory gaming experience. It has 4D Game vibration, Picture-in-Picture, Do Not Disturb, and Esports Mode features to enhance your mobile gaming experience.
product_description.Multi Turbo 5.0: This feature improves system processor speed, data connection, and power-saving operation. It also has a liquid cooling solution for all five components to keep this smartphone cool.
product_description.Funtouch OS 11.1 (Based on Android 11): The Funtouch OS 11.1 has a clean design aesthetic along with touch controls to make it simple, practical, and user-friendly.
